text: Samdrup Jongkhar District (Dzongkha: བསམ་གྲུབ་ལྗོངས་མཁར་རྫོང་ཁག་; Wylie: Bsam- grub Ljongs-mkhar rdzong-khag) is one of the 20 districts in Bhutan. The administrative centre is Samdrup Jongkhar. There are eleven village blocks: * Dewathang Gewog * Gomdar Gewog * Langchenphu Gewog * Lauri Gewog * Martshala Gewog * Orong Gewog * Pemathang Gewog * Phuntshothang Gewog * Samrang Gewog * Serthi Gewog * Wangphu Gewog Category:Districts of Bhutan
title: Samdrup Jongkhar District
